name: CFStreamErrorHTTPAuthentication
desc: Authentication error codes that may be returned when trying to apply authentication to a request.

items.name: case typeUnsupported
items.desc: Specified authentication type is not supported.

items.name: case badUserName
items.desc: User name is in a format that is not suitable for the request. Currently, user names are decoded using kCFStringEncodingISOLatin1.

items.name: case badPassword
items.desc: Password is in a format that is not suitable for the request. Currently, passwords are decoded using kCFStringEncodingISOLatin1.
